Easily publish a preprint if you use #rstats #rmarkdown & GitHub:

* knit mypaper.Rmd to html
* rename mypaper.html -> index.html
* commit index.html & push to GitHub
* activate GitHub pages in repo settings

Voila! After a minute or two, your paper is now published.
